description:
Smoke effects appear across all sorts of models. Ranging from the Mortal Realms, all the way to the grim dark future. Maybe it’s from a spell, the end of a gun barrel, or of course, a smoke grenade. If you’re a Warhammer fan, you’re bound to come across smoke on a miniature eventually, and Ollie’s got you covered!
